a-a heart attack, a stroke?

278
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:35,481
They're not exactly sure yet.

279
00:13:35,482 --> 00:13:37,566
They ran a bunch of tests,
but we're still waiting.

280
00:13:37,567 --> 00:13:38,984
What do you mean?

281
00:13:38,985 --> 00:13:40,236
He collapsed.

282
00:13:40,237 --> 00:13:42,446
He fell down,
and he was unconscious.

283
00:13:42,447 --> 00:13:44,198
