00:14:07,973 --> 00:14:10,474
Then you should come home.

295
00:14:10,475 --> 00:14:12,101
[sighs]

296
00:14:12,102 --> 00:14:14,311
Okay, I'll, uh...

297
00:14:14,312 --> 00:14:17,022
I'll call you back when I have
my ticket information.

298
00:14:17,023 --> 00:14:19,483
