seen them for... well, years.

311
00:15:00,275 --> 00:15:02,735
I love it. That could
only happen in New York.

312
00:15:02,736 --> 00:15:04,320
Fuck. Shit.
I don't have my phone.

313
00:15:04,321 --> 00:15:06,280
