left it at brunch.

315
00:15:07,532 --> 00:15:08,741
We'll go back and get it.

316
00:15:08,742 --> 00:15:10,117
No, it's, like, ten blocks.
Just call it.

317
00:15:10,118 --> 00:15:11,243
Okay.

318
00:15:11,244 --> 00:15:13,662
This is, like,
the fifth time this month

319
00:15:13,663 --> 00:15:15,331
