this. We barely know each other.

348
00:16:43,420 --> 00:16:46,714
Okay. But, um, we just...

349
00:16:46,715 --> 00:16:47,924
Had sex?

350
00:16:49,092 --> 00:16:50,342
Uh, yes, we just had sex.

351
00:16:50,343 --> 00:16:52,721
But that doesn't mean
we know each other.

352
00:16:53,805 --> 00:16:56,141
You're right. I'm sorry.

353
00:16:58,852 --> 00:17:01,687
Honestly, I-I think
you should just go.

354
00:17:01,688 --> 00:17:03,897
Oh. Okay.

355
00:17:03,898 --> 00:17:05,108
Let me just...

356
