do you want to take a shower?

373
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:58,535
Are you-you hungry? 'Cause
I could, I could get something

374
00:17:58,536 --> 00:18:00,871
- and...
- That-that is very sweet
of you, thank you.

375
00:18:00,872 --> 00:18:03,792
Come here. I'm so sorry.

376
00:18:07,337 --> 00:18:09,046
Okay.

377
00:18:09,047 --> 00:18:11,381
I'm sorry, did I,
did I do something wrong?

378
00:18:11,382 --> 00:18:14,219
No, no, not at all.
I just, uh...

379
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:21,016
I am gonna hop
in the shower, actually.

380
00:18:21,017 --> 00:18:22,392
That's a, that's a good idea.

381
00:18:22,393 --> 00:18:23,852
Good, good. Just show me
where your computer is

382
00:18:23,853 --> 00:18:25,354
and I'll-I'll book you a ticket.

383
00:18:25,355 --> 00:18:27,940
Robbie.

384
00:18:27,941 --> 00:18:29,650
[chuckles] I will handle that.

385
00:18:29,651 --> 00:18:31,777
We just had
this great night tonight

386
00:18:31,778 --> 00:18:32,986
